  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: how to work safely in care homes
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for those working in care homes providing information on how to work safely during this period of sustained transmission of COVID-19.</p>

  </div>
</div>

